descriptionHtml:
Spaces –offices, memberships, meeting rooms.

Upgrade your workplace and plug into our energy. Spaces offers offices, memberships and meeting rooms all in centrally located beautifully designed locations. Just choose the location that’s most convenient for you, book via our app and show up.

Any type of workspace:
Offices, memberships, meeting rooms. Pick the space that suits your needs.

Any duration:
Book by the hour, by the day, or upgrade to our unlimited Membership monthly subscription.

Easy to use:
Just book via the app and show up at the Spaces location.
